casebody.data:
Estate of Liposchak et al., Appellants, v. Conrad, Admr., Bureau of Workers’ Compensation, Appellee.

[Cite as Estate of Liposchak v. Conrad (2001), 90 Ohio St.3d 1248.]

(No. 00-839 Submitted November 14, 2000 Decided January 17, 2001.) Stewart Jajfy & Associates Co., L.P.A., Stewart R. Jaffy, Marc J. Jaffy and Eric S. Bravo, for appellants. Betty D. Montgomery, Attorney General, and Dennis H. Behm, Assistant Attorney General, for appellee.

The cause is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently allowed.

Moyer, C.J., Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cooic and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur. Douglas, J., dissents.
